{"tid":1082948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶師大教授　課堂講魯迅「損害國家聲譽」被撤職","createTime":"2019-03-29T09:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T10:59:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb06eb19ac6175cfb619abcc1d7866c9c055284","tid":1082948,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/teacher-12_R2t2g_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fteacher-12_R2t2g_1200x0.png&h=0eb34699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講魯迅損害國家聲譽？重慶師範大學宣布，副教授唐雲因在《魯迅研究》課程教學中，發表損害國家聲譽的言論，對師生造成不良影響，被撤銷教師資格和降級；唐雲個人微博內容已幾乎全部刪除或封禁，但網上流傳一幅他早前的發帖，指今次是他任教 33 年來第一次離開，「今天披著恥辱離去，明天我會戴著桂冠而來」，又表示自己的學生「並不都是猶大」，暗示自己被撤職是被學生舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tong_LFLof_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftong_LFLof_1200x0.png&h=8c377624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n56 歲的唐雲是重慶南川人，1986 年 7 月四川師範大學畢業後，在重慶師範大學文學院工作至今，1997 年 11 月被評為副教授，據該校 3 月 20 日的文件顯示，經調查發現，唐雲在 2 月底《魯迅研究》的課程教學中，發表損害國家聲譽言論，違反政治紀律和教師職業道德，對師生造成不良影響，大學校長辦公會研究後決定，報請重慶市教委，撤銷他的教師資格，但文件無透露唐雲，到底在課堂說了甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n前維權律師浦志強就在微博發文，指唐雲是他的好朋友，質疑唐雲在文學院講魯迅，竟然損害國家聲譽，「要麼其言論之尖銳刻薄超過了魯迅，要麼當今盛世比那十幾年的民國更不堪、或更不堪一擊」，他又稱唐雲失去教職「基於唐門高足舉報」，這教職只是「討飯的破碗」，沒有甚麼意思。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/重慶師大教授-課堂講魯迅-損害國家聲譽-被撤職/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E8%AA%B2%E5%A0%82%E8%AC%9B%E9%AD%AF%E8%BF%85-%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD-%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4%E8%81%B7%2F&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=9108e978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E8%AA%B2%E5%A0%82%E8%AC%9B%E9%AD%AF%E8%BF%85-%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD-%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4%E8%81%B7%2F&h=a04cdd43\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/重慶師大教授-課堂講魯迅-損害國家聲譽-被撤職/</a>"},{"pid":"1a2f33611dc67b79c428dc5ca45a4b7da921f0bf","tid":1082948,"uid":65074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"當今盛世比那十幾年的民國更不堪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同民國比? 憑咩"},{"pid":"70848fd936bde8e29def3921e1ea1e6f4c81ab30","tid":1082948,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"哀其不幸，怒其不爭。"},{"pid":"c172b275f6aa3036f5039616c2402e12c42fc1ef","tid":1082948,"uid":163350,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa6d29c4569d1bb39cc055a45ea37529203e5c4","tid":1082948,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:40:29.000Z","msg":"因為魯迅講既野同而家支蟈人一樣"},{"pid":"750056538cb7f3d88f84677489e979a09236781c","tid":1082948,"uid":245016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毛澤東:魯迅的方向，就是中華民族新文化的方向。<br />\n而家又話影響國家聲譽，立維尼年歸帝算啦。"},{"pid":"ef3210c81fe8dea9c5e889f038d39801b9eb5a42","tid":1082948,"uid":245016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"750056538cb7f3d88f84677489e979a09236781c","tid":1082948,"uid":245016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毛澤東:魯迅的方向，就是中華民族新文化的方向。<br />\n而家又話影響國家聲譽，立維尼年歸帝算啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"*稱"},{"pid":"3c547f0de302931ea0e85860e4e4f2b4e26a7f12","tid":1082948,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"文人？返鄉下耕田啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm